      "purpose": "v17 architecture + a new tile-level binary 'is this tile defect?' classification head, jointly trained with seg head. Aux loss is 0.1\u00d7 BCE on the aux logit. Intended for inference-time gating (Mode A soft multiply or Mode B hard gate) to reduce FPs on empty tiles.",
